1 Add algs4.jar package in Intellij Idea
    File -> Project Structure -> Project Settings -> Modules -> [ Your Project ] -> Dependencies -> [ Click "+" ] -> JARs or directories -> [ Find algs4.jar ] -> OK -> Apply

2 Compile java file with correct version
    Settings -> Build, Execution, Deployment -> Java Compiler -> Project bytecode version: -> 1.7 -> Apply -> OK

3. Run Commands:
    E:\Java\Algorithms\1\Assignment1\out\production\Assignment1>java -classpath ".;C:\Users\Aegis\algs4\algs4.jar" PercolationVisualizer input2.txt

4. Input file interpretation
    It get a very bad feeling when watching the input file in Windows, the
    2
    1 1
    2 2
    1 2
    will looks like 21 12 21 2 in Windows

